reviews.text: We ordered the dinner sets of lamb chop and risotto. Very delicious and very good value for money. Hope the restaurant can continue to operate without being pulled out of business due to rental increases by the landlord.

The breakfast is very nice at the decent price. The biggest problem is, that they say they are opened from 9.30, google says the same. OpenRice says 9am. Last time they opened 9.30, this time they told me its closed, opens from 10am.
Went there on a Wednesday night, not too crowded. Food was okay, a bit salty for me. The soup was good tho. Staff was friendly. Price was average, about $200 per person.

Came on a Saturday late morning, around 11, just in time to catch the breakfast menu. The breakfast meun is a steal! Highly recommend to come in the morning. Ordered eggs bendict with smoked salmon breakfast set, all day breakfast set and the deluxe breakfast. Although I feel like they could have serve a little more smoked salmon on each plate, the poached egg is cooked to perfection. The fries are chirpy but not dry. The salad dressing is cirtusy, which is very refreshing! The sausages are just average. If I have to be really picky, I will say the coffee has room to improve.

The place is pretty small and when it's packed it could seat around 30 people. There are only 2 servers, so you might not get the best service from them because they are always very busy, but when you ask them they are willing to serve. Will definitely recommend this place to others!

result.name: Chef's Movement

reviews.text:
五一勞動節, 庸懶既早上閒遊雞地搵食😪見到Chef movement有all day breakfast 咁附合不勞動既法則😛
 
舖頭座落係街角, 大玻璃窗加埋高樓底, 用盡咗天然光🌞營造咗舒適氣氛; 小小空間排咗20個位左右, 除左小角落部份, 全部都可以照到天然光, 呢啲餐廳我最鍾意, 影出黎既相係可以提昇一個層次📸
 
MENU相對簡單, 早餐、午餐、兩個ALL DAY BREAKFAST同埋SET DINNER; 先黎Deluxe all day breakfast; 塞滿一個大碟既早餐🍽️以炸薯條🍟居中, 腸仔同🌭橙🍊打翼, 煙三文魚🐟Benedit 打箭頭, 火腿同菜打後; 除咗樣靚外, 個班尼迪蛋都處理得好出色🍳切開時蛋漿係流出黎, 而蛋白則係全熟🥚
 
另外仲有墨魚汁🦑鮮魷扁意粉🍝跟餐上係有湯同沙律; 要提一提佢既沙律汁加入左柚小醬帶出酸中清新。而白色碟同墨魚汁既純黑形成對比, 黑到令面既汁包住意粉, 每啖都搞到牙黑嘴黑😬😬
 
餐飲都係跟嘢食送, 唔駛額外點☕🥛水準不過不失啦; 最後要提餐廳既小裝飾係深藍既牆身上掛住美國隊長既大盾🇺🇲回應番近日Avengers 4😚😚埋單兩個人160左右, 食物中上, 但個大玻璃窗, 坐係側邊真係好舒服🤗🤗
座位有點擠迫，食物味道跟賣相還不錯，可惜這次的芝士牛角包比之前少了很多芝士 :(

All day breakfast 👍🏻😋。
坐嘅位置比較狹窄。
食完要盡快離開 ..... 會腳痺。
地方小店，主要出品是意粉類，如以價錢與出品比較則較高，上菜慢。
